{
  "id": "6a29305d9ea441b8f0fd92d2",
  "title": "引き入れ",
  "created": 1781084256,
  "updated": 1781105967,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a29305d9ea441b8f0fd92d2",
      "text": "引き入れ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084256,
      "updated": 1781084256
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29305f00000000007669b1",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084256,
      "updated": 1781084262
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973300000000000f29064",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101360,
      "updated": 1781101360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973300000000000f29065",
      "text": "デライトにおいて、輪郭同士を関連付けるための操作",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101360,
      "updated": 1781101360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973300000000000f29066",
      "text": "具体的には[引き入れ操作]を参照",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101360,
      "updated": 1781101360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29306600000000007669b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084263,
      "updated": 1781084263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2972f50000000000f29057",
      "text": "[デライト]の基本的な操作",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101301,
      "updated": 1781101301
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2972f50000000000f29058",
      "text": "\tデライトはこの操作の他に「投稿」と「検索」ができればOK",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101301,
      "updated": 1781101301
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2972f50000000000f29059",
      "text": "\tScrapboxでいうところの[ブラケティング]に該当する操作だと思う[久住哲.icon][bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101301,
      "updated": 1781101301
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29306400000000007669b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781084261,
      "updated": 1781084261
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a3",
      "text": "要するに",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a4",
      "text": "\t投稿([輪郭])を他の投稿とリンクする",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a5",
      "text": "\t\t他の人の投稿にリプライするとき",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a6",
      "text": "\t\tある投稿の続きを書くとき",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a7",
      "text": "\t概念同士の関係性を表す",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29733d0000000000f290a8",
      "text": "\t\t例えば、「動物」という投稿の下に「哺乳類」という投稿を\"引き入れる\"など",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101374,
      "updated": 1781101374
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973420000000000f290a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101378,
      "updated": 1781101378
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29736f0000000000f290c0",
      "text": "参考",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101423,
      "updated": 1781101423
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29736f0000000000f290c1",
      "text": " https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.EDD2/1E63",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101423,
      "updated": 1781101423
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984815",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984816",
      "text": "引き入れ＝下位",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984817",
      "text": "引き入れられ＝上位",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984818",
      "text": " 「引き入れ」と「引き入れられ」がどっちがどっちなのか分からずイライラしたので、気にしないことにした[久住哲.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984819",
      "text": "\t 厳密に使うのが面倒くさいので「[輪括する]」で済ませがち[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781101511
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973b20000000000f291a8",
      "text": "  ※引き入れによって生まれる関係を[輪括]と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101490,
      "updated": 1781101497
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2984b70000000000f291aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781105847,
      "updated": 1781105967
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098481b",
      "text": "[久住哲.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098481c",
      "text": " 表示(戸惑う)",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098481d",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/c627cd3008f2ae0f1f73e5dc5eeeb1a1]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098481e",
      "text": " \t引き入れられをダブルクリックすると",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098481f",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/bb0c278df210a407248123f45c1709eb]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984820",
      "text": " \t逆になる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984821",
      "text": " \t引き入れをダブルクリックして戻す",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984822",
      "text": " \t要は引き入れは内側、引き入れられは外側",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984823",
      "text": " \tダブルクリックで切り替わる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984824",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984825",
      "text": "意外なことだが、[引き入れは必須ではない][zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984826",
      "text": " [知名]さえついていれば見つかる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984827",
      "text": "  Cosenseで[被リンクのないページ]が意外と見つかるのと似てる",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781101582
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2934d80000000000984830",
      "text": " 実際引き入れをほとんどしないデライターも居る",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085401,
      "updated": 1781085412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2934d80000000000984831",
      "text": "  n=1",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085401,
      "updated": 1781085412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2934d80000000000984832",
      "text": "  気軽な公開メモとしての運用と思われる[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085401,
      "updated": 1781085418
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2935120000000000984833",
      "text": " [輪郭は単なるメモ]なので、単体でも（まあ）成立する",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085458,
      "updated": 1781085555
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984828",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29738d0000000000f291a0",
      "text": "関連アイコン",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101454,
      "updated": 1781101454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29738d0000000000f291a1",
      "text": " [引き入れたい.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101454,
      "updated": 1781101454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29738d0000000000f291a2",
      "text": " [引き入れた.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101454,
      "updated": 1781101454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2984f20000000000f291ac",
      "text": " [引き入れ記号.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781105906,
      "updated": 1781105918
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29738d0000000000f291a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101454,
      "updated": 1781101454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973800000000000f2913b",
      "text": "[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101441,
      "updated": 1781101441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973800000000000f2913c",
      "text": " 既に[引き入れ（デライト）]があるのでマージしました",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101441,
      "updated": 1781101441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973800000000000f2913d",
      "text": "  被リンク先を確認して問題ないと判断",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101441,
      "updated": 1781101441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2973800000000000f2913f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781101441,
      "updated": 1781101441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e70000000000984829",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098482a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2933e7000000000098482b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781085160,
      "updated": 1781085160
    }
  ]
}